{"title":"Interest, penalties and surcharge: penalties: Appeals Review Unit (ARU)","public_updated_at":"2016-02-23T15:15:41Z","details":{"body":"<p>For appeals against fixed automatic penalties for tax years up to and including 2009-10 from customers dealt with in PT Operations, PAYE, and Self Assessment (PSA), the Appeals Review Unit (ARU) is</p>\n\n<p>HMRCs<br />\nLate Penalties and Excise team<br />\nFloor 2<br />\nHoward House<br />\nNottingham<br />\nNG2 1AB</p>\n\n<p>Different arrangements apply for Specialist PT and requests for review from customers dealt with by this directorate should not be sent to Howarde House.</p>\n\n<p>For cases within Local Compliance, the reviews will be undertaken by a Local Review Team. Other Business Units will have their own arrangements.</p>\n\n<p>For tax years 2010-11 onwards, for guidance see <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam61310\">SAM61310</a>.</p>\n","section_id":"SAM61064","breadcrumbs":[{"section_id":"SAM61000","base_path":"/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam61000"}],"child_section_groups":[],"manual":{"base_path":"/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual"}},"routes":[{"path":"/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam61064","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"hmrc-manuals-api","rendering_app":"manuals-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"hmrc_manual_section","schema_name":"hmrc_manual_section","first_published_at":"2016-04-08T16:37:06Z","base_path":"/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam61064","description":"","content_id":"8dcdaae6-d27e-5a90-a8cf-337e6b92fa5b","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D25","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/hm-revenue-customs","base_path":"/government/organisations/hm-revenue-customs","content_id":"6667cce2-e809-4e21-ae09-cb0bdc1ddda3","description":null,"document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","